<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>977</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 zhǔ yǐ jiāng shēng mìng de dào lù zhǐ shì wǒ, wǒ jiù bù pà zài zhè tiáo lù shàng shī luò.
 zhǔ zǒng shì yòng tā de shuāng shǒu yǐn lǐng wǒ, zhè me duō nián wǒ dōu jì dé.
 chūn xià qiū dōng guò, suì suì nián nián guò. zhǔ de cí ài suí shí péi bàn wǒ.
 wǒ yě xué huì, wǒ yě dǒng dé, yǒu huà jiù duì zhǔ shuō.
 rén dōu bù zhù wǒ, shén réng bāng zhù wǒ. lù shàng yǒu ma nǎ, tú zhōng yǒu shuǐ hē.
 yǒng gǎn xiàng qián zǒu, bù pà lù qū zhé. zhǔ de cí ài suí shí péi bàn wǒ.
 zhǔ de cí ài suí shí péi bàn wǒ.</lyrics>
<title>zhǔ yǐ jiāng shēng mìng de dào lù zhǐ shì wǒ 迦南977</title>
</song>